create_architecture_document.output_format:
Your output should be a complete {document_type} document in JSON format with the following structure:

```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "document_type": "{document_type}",
  "document": {
    "title": "Document Title",
    "version": "1.0",
    "sections": [
      {
        "title": "Section Title",
        "content": "Section content..."
      }
    ],
    "diagrams": [
      {
        "title": "Diagram Title",
        "description": "Diagram description..."
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

review_architecture.input_description:
You have been provided with:

1. Architecture Document(s): {documents_description}
2. Review Criteria: {criteria_description}

review_architecture.output_format:
Your review should be structured as follows:

```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "reviews": {
    "[document_name]": {
      "overall_assessment": "Brief overall assessment",
      "strengths": ["Strength 1", "Strength 2"],
      "concerns": ["Concern 1", "Concern 2"],
      "recommendations": ["Recommendation 1", "Recommendation 2"],
      "criteria_evaluation": {
        "[criterion]": {
          "rating": "Rating (1-5)",
          "comments": "Detailed comments"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

analyze_dependencies.input_description:
You have been provided with:

1. Module Definitions: {modules_description}
2. API Specifications: {apis_description}

analyze_dependencies.output_format:
Your dependency analysis should be structured as follows:

```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "analysis": {
    "summary": "Overall dependency analysis summary",
    "key_findings": ["Finding 1", "Finding 2"],
    "issues": [
      {
        "type": "Issue type (e.g., circular dependency)",
        "description": "Issue description",
        "components": ["Component1", "Component2"],
        "severity": "Severity level",
        "recommendation": "How to address this issue"
      }
    ],
    "dependency_matrix": [
      {
        "module": "Module name",
        "dependencies": ["Dependency1", "Dependency2"]
      }
    ],
    "optimization_strategies": ["Strategy 1", "Strategy 2"]
  }
}
```
